Title: Establishes a fetal and infant mortality review board
Summary: Establishes a fetal and infant mortality review board to study fetal and infant mortality and morbidity and make recommendations on policies, best practices, and strategies to reduce fetal and infant mortality and morbidity within New York city.
LawCode: Add ยง17-166.1, NYC Ad Cd
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the administrative code of the city of New York, in relation to establishing a fetal and infant mortality review board
